data.text:
2002

2 hr 0 mins

Drama, Family

NR

Watchlist

Mark's daughter Carol (Stacy Van Dyke) and her newlywed husband disappear from a remote California town. Mark believes they may be victims of foul play after some of the locals start acting suspiciously and a potential witness is murdered. Campbell: Frederick Coffin. Kelly: Molly Hagan. Antoine: Faran Tahir. Mark: Dick Van Dyke.
